HEADWORD: By-end
<hw>By"-end`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Private end or
interest; secret purpose; selfish advantage.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>bye-end</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>⟦ldquo⟧Profit or some other <qex>by-end</qex>.⟦rdquo⟧</q>
<rj><qau>L'Estrange.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bygone</ent>⟦br⟧
